name: W. Frank Ableson
description: Husband, Father, Entrepreneur, Software Engineer and Author. My most recent book project is Android in Action, which is an update to Unlocking Android, published by Manning. I also contributed to a couple of Glenn Bachmann's Palm OS books a number of years ago.

name: Charlie Collins
description: Software craftsman and engineering team builder, speaker, and author.

name: Eric Elliot
description: Eric Elliott is the author of Programming JavaScript Applications (O'Reilly), & host of the documentary film, Programming Literacy. He has contributed to software experiences for Adobe Systems, Zumba Fitness, The Wall Street Journal, ESPN, BBC, and top recording artists including Usher, Frank Ocean, Metallica, and many more. He spends most of his time in the San Francisco bay area with the most beautiful woman in the world.
